review:
Dr.chahal clinic is just awesome..the doctors and staff at viveknagar branch are so dedicated to their work. Dr. Shilpee and team work tirelessly with smile .
I visited many other clinic for my gum rescission and they told take out multiple teeth. However doctor Chahal gave good review and avoided unnecessary tooth extraction.
They gave good consulting of the treatment and adviced good opinion of caps..
The entire treatment was seamless experience.
Doctor Shilpee takes special care of each patient as if they are her own..
The staff also very quick and always ready to serve the patients...
Doctor Chahal himself is very simple and humble doctor.
They are very considerate of patients financial situation and help patients the best, with cost effective treatment.
I am very much happy of the treatment.
Thanks to Doctor Chahal, doctor Shilpee and the staff at viveknagar branch.
They do offer many other astestics treatment.
